```plantuml
@startuml solenya-group_solenya

actor User
participant App
participant Component
participant Router
participant Validator
participant Storage
participant TimeTravel
participant VirtualDOM

User -> App: Initializes application
App -> Component: Creates root component
Component -> VirtualDOM: Renders initial view
VirtualDOM --> Component: Returns virtual DOM tree
Component -> App: Passes rendered view
App -> VirtualDOM: Patches real DOM

User -> Component: Triggers action (e.g., form submit)
Component -> Validator: Validates input
Validator --> Component: Returns validation result
Component -> Storage: Serializes state
Storage --> Component: Confirms persistence
Component -> VirtualDOM: Updates view
VirtualDOM --> Component: Returns updated virtual DOM
Component -> App: Notifies update
App -> VirtualDOM: Patches real DOM

User -> Router: Navigates to new route
Router -> Component: Loads new component
Component -> VirtualDOM: Renders new view
VirtualDOM --> Component: Returns virtual DOM tree
Component -> App: Passes rendered view
App -> VirtualDOM: Patches real DOM

User -> TimeTravel: Triggers time travel
TimeTravel -> Storage: Retrieves historical state
Storage --> TimeTravel: Returns serialized state
TimeTravel -> Component: Applies historical state
Component -> VirtualDOM: Renders historical view
VirtualDOM --> Component: Returns virtual DOM tree
Component -> App: Passes rendered view
App -> VirtualDOM: Patches real DOM

@enduml
```